      <hedline>
        <hl1>Arts, Briefly; Footnote</hl1>
        <hl2 class="online_headline">An ‘Addams Family’ Musical</hl2>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By CAMPBELL ROBERTSON; Compiled by Lawrence Van Gelder</byline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A musical of ''The Addams Family'' is in the works, with a planned premiere on Broadway in the 2009-10 season. Marshall Brickman and Rick Elice (''Jersey Boys'') are writing the book, Andrew Lippa (''The Wild Party'') is writing the score and Julian Crouch and Phelim McDermott (''Shockheaded Peter'') will direct and design.</p>
        <p>CAMPBELL ROBERTSON</p>
      </block>
